IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: LIST OF EXHIBITS CyberTip 166823248 CyberTip169498082 NARRATIVE On 8/22/2023 the Maryland State Police Internet Crimes Against Children (ICAC) task force received CyberTips: 166823248 169498082 from the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC). The CyberTip, which was reported by Instagram, was generated by the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC) due to Instagram reporting on 7/17/2023 at 17:22:14 UTC a user on Instagram distributed child pornography. Instagramprovided the following information: CYBERTIP166823248 Name: hola Date of Birth: 11-03-2006 Approximate Age: 16 Email Address: gamingwithboi2007@gmail.com (Verified) Email Address: gamingwithiyan@gmail.com Email Address: gamingwitheric07@gmail.com (Verified) Screen/User Name: fw.eri2 ESP User ID: 44510720032 IP Address: 2601:14b:4584:53b0:c1f0:13ee:6caa:a4c2 (Login) 07-17-2023 17:38:48 UTC Prior CT Reports: 153270236 CHAT Sent in product: Instagram Direct Files unique ESP Identifier: 204552682239261 Messenger Thread Name: Datkidd.manman Messenger Thread ID: 17895641534819718 The following messages were sent immediately preceding and following the uploaded CEI: (July 17, 2023 at 17:20:18 UTC) 54483779717: Wat u got (July 17, 2023 at 17:20:34 UTC) 44510720032: Um let me look (July 17, 2023 at 17:20:41 UTC) 54483779717: K (July 17, 2023 at 17:22:14 UTC) 17841444400973840: This image was uploaded *described below* (July 17, 2023 at 17:22:56 UTC) 54483779717: Videos too Uploaded July 17, 2023 at 17:22:14 UTC Two files were associated with the CyberTip. TFC Mueller reviewed both files and observed one to contain child pornography. Listed below is a description of the file. File Name: wg1fW7L6UAOMLwX4361670701_204552688905927_316625318924509 1270_o.jpg Description: This color image depicts two prepubescent males exposing their genitals in a vehicle. Upload: 2601:14b:4584:53b0:c1f0:13ee:6caa:a4c2 on 07-17-2023 at 17:22:14 UTC CYBERTIP 16948082 Date of Birth: 11-03-2006 Approximate Age: 16 Email Address: gamingwithboi2007@gmail.com (Verified) Screen/User Name: unknown57470 ESP User ID: 53737617722 IP Address: 2607:fb91:1611:f45e:7dda:8493:bdb7:e237 (Login) 08-01-2023 06:25:59 UTC Fourteen files were associated with the CyberTip. TFC Mueller received the files and observed four to contain child pornography. Listed below is a description of two files. File Name:hFuj7piEGqpc9hWj358990597_636354701895308_5513406636865845965_n.jpg Description: This color image depicts a prepubescent males genitals. File Name:wKBAJhd9GzTdTAbp358764022_647260070666909_339209307125420583_o.jpg Description:This color image depicts a prepubescent males genitals. A check, through Maxmind, of the associated Upload IP address shows the IP address is registered through Comcast and geolocates to Mount Rainier, MD. On 9/11/2023 TFC Mueller authored a subpoena, upload IP address (2601:14b:4584:53b0:c1f0:13ee:6caa:a4c2) subscriber information, and submitted it to the Howard County States Attorneys Office for endorsement. Case Open, investigation ongoing.

LIST OF EXHIBITS Endorsed Comcast Subpoena NARRATIVE On 9/18/2023 TFC Mueller received the endorsed Comcast Subpoena. On 9/18/2023 TFC Mueller submitted the subpoena to Comcast. Case Open, investigation ongoing.

LIST OF EXHIBITS Comcast Subpoena Response NARRATIVE On 9/25/2023 TFC Mueller received the Comcast Subpoena response. Comcast provided the following information: Subscriber Name: SAKAYA FRASIER Service Address: 3601 55TH AVE APT 2,LANDOVER HILLS, MD 20784 Billing Address: 3601 55TH AVE APT 2,LANDOVER HILLS, MD 20784 Telephone #: (202) 621-4561 Type of Service: Internet Account Number: 8299420602756978 Account Status: Active IP Assignment: Dynamically Assigned Private Network IP Lease Length: See Enclosed E-mail User Ids: sakayafrazier2@comcast.net Case Open, pending knock and talk.

On 1/5/2024 TFC Mueller and Cpl. Heid, of the Maryland State Police Child Recovery Unit, responded to3601 55th Avenue #2 Hyattsville, MD 20784, to conduct a knock and talk. Once on scene, investigators made contact with Lavay Lawrence, the spouse of Sakaya Frasier. The two live together in the apratemnt alone. Lavay stated Eric is his 16 year old little brother. Lavay provided investigators with their mother, Shennell Proctor, contact information (202-427-5245). Investigators contacted Shennell who was informed of the investigation and was provided and educational internet safety talk, to relay to her son. Case closed, by exception.
